title: Drinker's VIP Lounge - Chris Jericho
description:
We're breaking down the walls tonight as I interview wrestling legend Chris Jericho about his three-decade career in the business, his work in Hollywood and his upcoming graphic novel project, PAINMAKER. 

Find out more about Painmaker here: https://thepainmakerproject.com
